00:04:32.760 --> 00:04:38.090
Some function of t, times
some function of x, OK?

00:04:38.090 --> 00:04:43.600
And the text uses, look for
solutions u(x,t) that are

00:04:43.600 --> 00:04:44.340
of this form.

00:04:44.340 --> 00:04:50.460
Some function of t,
and I didn't remember.

00:04:50.460 --> 00:04:56.450
Ah yes, it's A(x)B(t).

00:04:56.450 --> 00:04:59.450
OK, that's what I
