00:05:02.470 --> 00:05:05.770
And when we go to match
the initial condition,

00:05:05.770 --> 00:05:09.840
I'll just plug in t=0
and I'll see the A(x)'s.

00:05:09.840 --> 00:05:12.280
Well, what are they?

00:05:12.280 --> 00:05:15.260
In this case, so their
eigenfunction-- oh,

00:05:15.260 --> 00:05:18.020
I have to tell you about the
